POLOKWANE – Conditions are expected to clear in Polokwane from Thursday onwards as the week starts off with partly cloudy conditions and mild temperatures. People’s Weather’s forecast suggests cool to mild maximum temperatures this week, ranging from 20ºC on Wednesday and Saturday to 21ºC on Monday, Tuesday, Thursday, Friday and Sunday.  While partly cloudy conditions are expected, no rain has been forecast for the week. Minimum temperatures will range from 7ºC to 11ºC. 